**Bottom line:** D3D11 needs ~370 discards/frame to be Ã¢â‚¬Å“merely playableÃ¢â‚¬Â because the over-charge accounting **manufactures** a discard storm that accidentally mimics aggressive GPU fencing. D3D9 never enters that regime.

