## 5. Minimal correct fix (ranked, with exact changes)

**Do not ship per-generation ring buffers.** The capture-invisible Ã¢â€ â€™ deterministic transition is strong evidence that approach is wrong.

### Fix A (minimum blast radius Ã¢â‚¬â€ do these two first)

**A1. Mirror D3D9 accounting** in `Direct3d11_DynamicVertexBufferData.cpp`:

